PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1983-2008, which transferred from the Minister of Transport to the Minister of Fisheries and Oceans the management, charge and direction of three parcels of land at Owen Sound, Ontario, Leamington, Ontario and Cap-aux-Meules, Quebec, deleting all references to Cap-aux-Meules.
